    privacyTitle: "Privacy",
    privacyDeclarationTitle: "Privacy Policy",
    privacySection1Title: "1. Privacy at a glance",
    privacySection1GeneralTitle: "General information",
    privacySection1GeneralText: "The following information provides a simple overview of what happens to your personal data when you visit this website. Personal data is all data with which you can be personally identified. Detailed information on the subject of data protection can be found in our privacy policy listed below this text.",
