    privacySection1ChangesText: "From 2025, new regulations on consent management come into force, enabling centralized management of cookie preferences. In addition, parts of the EU AI regulation become effective, regulating certain AI practices. We always keep our data protection measures up to date.",
    privacySection2Title: "2. Data collection on this website",
    privacySection2ResponsibleTitle: "Who is responsible for data collection on this website?",
    privacySection2ResponsibleText: "Data processing on this website is carried out by the website operator. You can find their contact details in the 'Information on the responsible party' section of this privacy policy.",
